Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Alexey Spiridonov <alexey@spiridonov.dev>
Description: MCP server for Ubuntu syslog
 Go MCP server for reading and searching Ubuntu syslog.
 Supports filtering by date range, wildcard patterns, pagination,
 transport-level access-key authentication, and optional response encryption.
